{"tid":2226192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南丫海難8周年 警員斥悼念市民做戲消費意外","createTime":"2020-10-02T00:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T03:49:01.000Z","uid":49776,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e404e6d8d3d26f0ddc15127ec66d1721b704870d","tid":2226192,"uid":49776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T00:47:11.000Z","msg":"南丫海難8周年 警員斥悼念市民做戲消費意外<br />\n今日是南丫海難8周年，晚上有市民在中環碼頭進行悼念祭祀。有防暴警員到場，指悼念的市民撒溪錢影響道路整潔，雙方一度爭執，警員曾斥責市民不要做戲消費意外。在場市民繼續悼念，警員其後指她無戴口罩，向她發出告票。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2359872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2359872&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAiukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=29e89246\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2359872</a>"},{"pid":"5c75b66d6be7ffb53ec7c0d62dd3adc203df069f","tid":2226192,"uid":143343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T00:49:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9410557d7dd0b722a6694519baa9f3154666321","tid":2226192,"uid":49776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:01:05.000Z","msg":"南丫海難8周年︱涼薄警嘲祭品垃圾 譏市民做戲悼亡魂 陰濕伸腳撠記者<br />\n<br />\n有便衣警聲稱拜祭用的紙錢是垃圾，又稱雷「做戲」、「消費意外」，並在儀式完成後，向尊重死者而除罩拜祭的雷發告票，稱她違反「口罩令」。其間雷一度情緒激動，反斥警員「冇人性」，「係咪立咗國安法，連南丫海難都唔准拜？」，表明來年會繼續拜祭，希望港人出席悼念。該名便衣警又刻意伸腳，企圖絆倒在場採訪的網媒女記者。幸女記者反應快速，及時跳過「警腿」才未有被絆倒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/KSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FKSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY%2F&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAiukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=8bca2f2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FKSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY%2F&h=e1933378\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/KSVN7UMHCFF6TKB6QHFXEZTSGY/</a>"},{"pid":"32679afb9c2b430c71730afca9c4972fc9904eef","tid":2226192,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:02:30.000Z","msg":"真係咁憎我地咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f249bdb3a83231a458d93e6f989efa1fa4c617","tid":2226192,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:30:02.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44bf7b9b4c42398e7b204487a051b810c4bddc1","tid":2226192,"uid":242921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:42:03.000Z","msg":"以後民建聯唔好消費南京大屠殺/918事變等等。"},{"pid":"50418de23f84a0a016c919c2786333e60ba35528","tid":2226192,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:47:22.000Z","msg":"完全反人類呢班仆街零同理心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ba9db8c79f35b5f9f3333ee77160d2e987e64c","tid":2226192,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T03:49:01.000Z","msg":"中共悼念抗日戰爭死難者係做戲消費意外"}]}